* SN-26-bridge-coverage-a — exercises the new NMD4 fire-point in CSNOBOL4
* monitor bridge:
*   NMD4 (pattern .-capture commit) → monitor_emit_value
*
* Drive via:
*   MONITOR_READY_PIPE=...  MONITOR_GO_PIPE=...  MONITOR_NAMES_OUT=... \
*       /home/claude/csnobol4/snobol4 -bf probe_c.sno
*
* Expected wire (3 records):
*   #0 VALUE  S         STRING(5)='AXBYC'      (ASGNVV — plain assignment)
*   #1 VALUE  captured  STRING(1)='A'          (NMD4   — pattern .-capture)
*   #2 END
*
* The middle record is the new one — proves NMD4 fires on a successful
* match's ANY('AB') . captured commit point.

        S = 'AXBYC'
        S ANY('AB') . captured
END
